sentences.english: The basic characteristics of the soil seed bank in flood plain grassland of the Fen River in Taiyuan region were investigated and studied.

sentences.english: To know about the eutrophic condition of present Fenhe Second reservoir.
sentences.chinese: 瞭解汾河二庫水體現階段的富營養狀況。

sentences.english: The Shanxi plain is watered by the Fen River which runs through it.
sentences.chinese: 山西平元由流經這裏的汾河灌溉。
